headline: 2 Top Tech Stocks to Buy in November
summary: Shares of Micron Technology (NASDAQ: MU) rose to a high of $157 earlier this year before pulling back to around $100 at the time of this writing.  Micron has seen a sharp rebound in its revenue over the last year.  In its fiscal 2024 fourth quarter, which ended Aug. 29, revenue jumped 93% year over year, showing the company's growth accelerating.
